@node intro "PhoneBook Version 1.00   Introduction"

PhoneBook was designed to be a small, quick and easy to use phone number
database program.

PhoneBook will allow you to store as many records as you have memory for.
The actual size of each record depends on the amount of info you type for
each record.

I've also included some example databases for you to browse. One of which
is all the Eden distributrion site's BBS numbers. There is also the tutorial
database created in the @{"Quick Tutorial" link quick} section.
@endnode
@node share "PhoneBook Version 1.00   Shareware"

