As such, i've decided to make PhoneBook shareware. I dont expect to be paid
much for PhoneBook as its such a small utility.

The fee for PhoneBook is 5ukp in the UK and 10ukp if you live outside of the
UK. Please send cash only in uk pounds. A cheque will ONLY be accepted if it
was drawn from a UK bank. I wont except postal/money orders. If you must
send foreign currencey, make sure that the amount after conversion still
equals 10 pounds. The extra 5 pound is to cover postage.

Send your registrations to:

